text: The Annedal Church () is a church building in Annedal in Gothenburg in Sweden. It belongs to the Gothenburg Annedal Parish of the Church of Sweden. Construction begun in 1908. The church was opened on Thanksgiving Day, 25 September 1910 by bishop Edvard Herman Rodhe. == References == ==Other websites== Category:Church of Sweden churches Category:Churches in Gothenburg
title: Annedal Church
